Welcome to Verify uuid’s documentation!¶

Documentation structure¶

Start your first steps with the Tutorials. In addition to setting up the tool, you will be shown some application examples.

In the How-To Guides , specific questions are solved with step-by-step instructions, e.g. How do I check a UUID?

The technical background to UUIDs is explained in the Explanation section.

The Reference area contains the technical description of the Soure Code.
